join TestNpc center
if {met_shizu}:
	TestNpc: ...You again.
	TestNpc: I still don't know what a Fallowhearted is.
	TestNpc: Maybe it's someone who follows their heart?
	TestNpc: Or maybe Cinderblock just made it up.
else:
	TestNpc: I am Shizukana Ito.
	TestNpc: I play the Erhu.
	TestNpc: ...you can leave now.
	[signal arg="flag:met_shizu"]
leave --All--
